	}
	[text*]
	{
		choice = more;
	  i order = 1;
		screen_text = "The pay is still worth it thought. I tried farming before, but I was not really good at it. My crops barely survived and I could barely get by. Joining the guard seemed thrilling, but look at me now. I feel like I reached new bottom now.";
